{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the role of a small slime on an epic journey through the Tower of Slimes. Immerse yourself in a world filled with diverse slimes and unique environments. With no prior knowledge, let the tower's caretaker guide you as you discover who you are and why you were created. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/InteractionEN.png?t=1737067841\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a universe rich in interactions and stories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/Respawn.png?t=1737067841\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you progress, learn new abilities: shoot fireballs, stick to walls, and master the powers of the elements scattered throughout the tower \u2014 fire, ice, earth, plant, lightning, and poison \u2014 each with its own unique characteristics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/Transform.png?t=1737067841\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Uncover the mysteries within the Tower of Slimes, a place transformed by its inhabitants. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/FireEnemy.png?t=1737067841\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover unique landscapes with specific mechanics for each map, find hidden locations, and engage in special interactions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/FireLocation.png?t=1737067841\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create your own story with meaningful choices, conversing with NPCs of each element. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/GreenSlime.png?t=1737067841\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With your adaptive abilities, face challenging bosses and various enemies. Survive battles, grow stronger, and unveil the secrets of this fascinating world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/Boss.png?t=1737067841\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3143310?t=1737067841","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3143310?t=1737067841","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/f2371d717f8a85a770b6ce64a6f5a45196772ed3/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737067841","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/f2371d717f8a85a770b6ce64a6f5a45196772ed3/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737067841","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3146230,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the role of a small slime on an epic journey through the Tower of Slimes. Immerse yourself in a world filled with diverse slimes and unique environments. With no prior knowledge, let the tower's caretaker guide you as you discover who you are and why you were created. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.st